<body>
    {%include "components/navbar.html.jinja"%}
    <br>
    <h1 class="text-center">FAQ's!</h1>
        <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto">
            <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py">What is Hand in Hand?</h5>
            <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color"> 
                <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
                <h5 class="text-color-2">
                Hand in hand is a web apllication in which we aim to create a place where people with disabilities can go 
                places without worrying about accessibiltiy as this web application allows users to create posts about
                places regarding changes in the accessability options.</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto">
            <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py">What safety precautions are there for kids using this site?</h5>
            <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color">
                <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
                <h5 class="text-color-2">
                For the children, parental permission is needed in order to hire a caretaker, 
                ensuring safety for both parties.</h5>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto">
            <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py">Are caretakers on this site verfied?</h5>
            <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color">
                <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
                <h5 class="text-color-2">
                We ensure all of our Caretakers list their training and experience in order for users to decide which are best 
                suited for them.

            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <hr class="h-card-text-color-sd p-2">
 
        <footer>
            <h1>Additonal Questions?</h1>
            <h2 class="purple-text">Contact Us!</h2>
        

            <div class="container text-center">
                <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
                    <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
                        <div class="col-md-auto">
                            <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Username">
                            <input type="text" id="message" placeholder="Message">
                            <button id="sendBtn" class="btn h-button-color">Send</button>
                        </div>
                    <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>



        </footer>





